title: Trump calls FBI raid on personal attorney disgraceful
text:
Trump calls FBI raid on personal attorney disgraceful 11:29am BST - 02:03 
U.S. President Donald Trump said on Monday that the FBI's raid on the office and home of his personal attorney Michael Cohen was a disgraceful action and a total witch hunt.
